item.title: Parkour Run
item.description: Run along rooftops, jump through windows, hang from ledges, and slide under giant water tanks. Perform various cool parkour inspired tricks using various vectors and angles, but be careful not to fall! How far can you go in this endless runner platformer game? Features: Exciting and fast paced music beats Simple minimalist graphics and urban style Addictive and repetitive gameplay, perfect for high score seekers Desktop and mobile friendly controls
